channel.title: Making a source, need help on one thing
channel.description:
I know how to edit the source, ect. Now you have Player Rights = 0 1 - Mod 2 - Staff 3 - Admin. What is it for Owner? Because some servers say 'Owner commands' but then you'd have to set it to admin, and then you can't use? If someone can help me, please do.
- Owner of PloxieScape-- Http://ploxiescape.co.nr
